- Encrypted user credentials
- Secure data storage
- Regular security audits

Despite our efforts, no system is 100% secure. Please keep your login credentials confidential.

## 5. Your Rights & Choices
You have the right to:
- Access, edit, or delete your account data.
- Opt out of marketing communications.
- Request a copy of your personal data.

To exercise these rights, contact us at **privacy@esaysay.com**.

## 6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Significant changes will be notified via email or platform alerts.

